        <num>CC 2757</num>
        <heading>2757.  Agreement to furnish work or materials or both</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2757.  Agreement to furnish work or materials or both.
A person, who undertakes to make a work, may agree, either to furnish his work and industry alone, or to furnish also the materials necessary for such a work.</p>
        </content>
